{
  "stem": "13981.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And well, it had been converted to hold 9,000 troops.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were 17 of us in a state's cabin that was built for two.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we made it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "England.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then from Glasgow, I went-- we were sent to Litchfield Barracks, which is near Birmingham, England.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from there, I was flown to Paris.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Paris had already fallen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from Paris-- we spent about a week or so in Paris, or less-- we was-- went by a truck to Baccarat, the famous glass place, with the fine glass.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, it was down at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there I joined the 103rd Division, 409th regiment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- the 409th regiment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Baccarat.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from there, we went fighting all across-- well, across France, Alsace-Lorraine, into Germany, and finally Innsbruck.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the day armistice was signed, we were in [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Schwarz, ?] Tirol or Austria, which was some 20, 30 miles east of Innsbruck.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, this-- this-- well, this was all across-- our duty is-- was to interrogate the prisoners of war to find out the enemy positions, so we could relay that to our division, so that they could make the proper plans for attacks or defense, or whatever it happened to be.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--so mine was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--interrogation of prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a carbine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we hardly ever used it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it-- ours was not so much of a front-line activity.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Though we had some of it, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was to get the prisoners of war, interrogate them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as I said, find out what the German positions were so we could relay that information to higher echelons.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there was one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was towards the end of the war, on the Siegfried line.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then let's start in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
